          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "### ✅ Use Built-in Connector\r\n\r\nBuilt-in connectors in Microsoft Sentinel are preconfigured integrations that enable quick, secure, and automated data ingestion from Microsoft and third-party services without custom development.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n**Why this recommendation:**\r\nYour data source is listed in Content Hub (Q1: {Q1}) and has a built-in connector (Q2: {Q2}). This is the fastest path — no custom development, no infrastructure to maintain.\r\n\r\n**Why not the alternatives?**\r\n- All other methods (CCF, Logs API, AMA, Logstash, Pipeline) require more setup and maintenance\r\n- Built-in connectors are Microsoft-supported and automatically updated\r\n\r\n**Constraints:**\r\n- Some built-in connectors require specific permissions (e.g., Global Admin for Microsoft 365)\r\n- Connector configuration may require API keys or OAuth consent from the vendor",
